title: Week 15 Preview: Star Wars, Game Wars, and Lock Wars
itunes:title: Week 15 Preview: Star Wars, Game Wars, and Lock Wars
description:
A room filled with heroes- Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Gregg Rosenthal and Chris Wesseling- get you ready for Week 15 of the NFL season, starting with a recap of Thursday night's Broncos/ Colts matchup (1:00) The heroes fight for their locks of the week and react to Brown’s GM John Dorsey’s comments about not having real players ( 27;57). Dan requests the full song of Team of ATL to rock out to. (51:10) Plus, much more!
